This document explains the complete wiring of ARACHNOID,
a 12-DOF quadruped robot that uses an Arduino Nano, MPU6050 IMU, OLED display, Bluetooth module, 
servo expansion board, and a BMS-protected Li-ion battery, enabling self-balancing using a PID control system.

